    schema1:description "Steve Barclay was Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs between 13 November 2023 and 5 July 2024. He was previously Secretary of State for Health and Social Care between 25 October 2022 and 13 November 2023. He held the same role between 5 July 2022 and 6 September 2022."@en ;
